headline: Pfizer Boasts Strong Oncology Portfolio: Can it Sustain Growth?
summary: PFE's oncology portfolio, boosted by Seagen and late-stage pipeline assets, may fuel growth amid lackluster stock performance.

headline: 2 Reasons to Watch MRK and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Shareholders of Merck would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 20.3% and now trades at $79.30. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
